<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.10">
<l>maṉṉutaṇ poḻilum vāviyum matiḷum māṭamā ḷikaiyumaṇ ṭapamum</l>
<l>teṉṉaṉtoṇ ṭaiyarkkōṉ ceytanaṉ mayilait tiruvallik kēṇiniṉ ṟāṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉinaṉ māṭa maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ</l>
<l>kāmaru cīrkkali kaṉṟi</l>
<l>coṉṉacoṉ mālai pattuṭaṉ vallār cukamiṉi tāḷvarvā ṉulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this word garland with ten [verses] composed by Kalikaṉṟi</l>
<l rend="indent">of desired esteem,</l>
<l>Leader of those of Maṅkai with fine impregnable mansions,</l>
<l rend="indent">to the one who stands in Tiruvallikkēṇi in fair Māyilai,</l>
<l>Built by the king of the Toṇṭais, a king of the south,</l>
<l rend="indent">[having] thick cool groves, stepwells,  walls, mansions, and pavilions,</l>
<l>They will rule the heavenly world with sweet joy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
